  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>행택, 헤더택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0757ca03-6029-4d59-9c9c-c30cca2358c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a3cd5f1a-77a1-48ca-94ef-7fb910a0640f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fc378dca-000e-4ed8-9d6b-011df2bfb38f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>진심</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-412a281c-16c5-421f-b445-37d6cc97384f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfODMg/MDAxNzQ4MTQyODUzNTY4.AVveEg4Z9Xd6-xHwyiZeFalfp_mWnTA-UQpqzYN6v2Eg.kCnOUxRnJuM67kuIqg_52rkodDTcQHE3pP4R6j8Z6uQg.PNG/5.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfODMg/MDAxNzQ4MTQyODUzNTY4.AVveEg4Z9Xd6-xHwyiZeFalfp_mWnTA-UQpqzYN6v2Eg.kCnOUxRnJuM67kuIqg_52rkodDTcQHE3pP4R6j8Z6uQg.PNG/5.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">행택은 기본 모양과 최소 수량으로 제작 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>택(Tag)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 보통 의류에 부착되는 기본 설명서 같은 부재제입니다. 물론 설명서라고 말하기는 그렇지만 공간의 배치와 디자인에 따라 제품의 기본적인 설명을 자세하게도 명확하게도 넣을 수 있습니다. 택의 종류는 무척이나 다양합니다. 또한 모양도 너무나 자유롭게 제작이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef38a66e-dcc4-452c-bdc5-b11cd57519d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa5412e9-a416-4c4d-b835-b68381c21797\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea05e41d-d859-4828-9d6e-ba08ee14dbaf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-84ef6502-9f89-4b53-837d-e2cb39cf9ce7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 기본적인 형태와 수량을 정하는 것이 좋습니다. 기본적인 형태로만 만들어도 단가를 많이 절약할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbb5da37-abcf-491f-a639-9862dc54a36a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8885683b-e387-452c-ba7c-9b09c6d559ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8b23025-12de-4932-bc8a-92a7bb0e2051\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dc69ba82-dd86-46c4-b54e-39ba93da31b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본적인 형태는 일단 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-573cb9cf-abd2-4e30-9006-9ced5797e277\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>사각형</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1efc0b3d-898f-49c8-bdc5-5b27de217da9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-55d1c815-741b-4439-a149-578bc4fe0a76\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-55d1c815-741b-4439-a149-578bc4fe0a76\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfMjg5/MDAxNzQ4MTQzNTU2NzA2.inhlyOlxSENI-36qYA4YzWnuy2SA-Z5WbAwrTyRfjbYg.hOMPQi4hz7oTn5gnppZ9t6ql3BcIxRgm9C-k85QGh6Qg.PNG/SE-55d1c815-741b-4439-a149-578bc4fe0a76.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"684\", \"originalHeight\" : \"504\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfMjg5/MDAxNzQ4MTQzNTU2NzA2.inhlyOlxSENI-36qYA4YzWnuy2SA-Z5WbAwrTyRfjbYg.hOMPQi4hz7oTn5gnppZ9t6ql3BcIxRgm9C-k85QGh6Qg.PNG/SE-55d1c815-741b-4439-a149-578bc4fe0a76.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25a611e3-1fa6-4f91-a34f-4e40ac40361a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28916f8f-948a-43c7-8028-9bbe828b3361\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0349de2-6215-4dad-b2a6-1af96976b20c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사각형 형태는 가장 저렴한 모양입니다. 이 형태는 굳이 도무송을 하지 않아도 제작할 수 있습니다. 일반 재단으로 만들고 타공으로 제작하면 가장 저렴하게 택을 만들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aae5795a-9a3c-4fd7-9ee4-e1ec886259db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dacb10a4-35f9-4dc5-a0ef-45e0b6b41c17\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f02e40c3-9d8e-41d4-a1e1-277c022b4b61\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b21bb2d-1608-4319-a556-e26d4e24d681\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 이렇게 만든 택에는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6c1611a-455a-45d8-8dfc-fa14fcf26da0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>단점</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ac22bdd-c753-408d-b6ef-c44f9903b52c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce2c47c4-f743-4486-9f63-877c37663883\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b339a51d-c7dc-495d-a6e6-d6eac9b6697f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac67e1b1-5318-4d4e-8fed-a90847dbac8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb7096b0-42f9-459d-a454-a24fd040179a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 하나는 재단의 정밀성입니다. 보통의 경우 택은 사이즈가 작습니다. 일반 재단은 4cm까지만 가능합니다. 그 이하의 재단은 일반 재단으로 불가능합니다. 그러므로 3.5cm 사이즈는 재단으로는 제작이 안되고 도무송(톰슨)으로 만들어야 합니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0539be62-6a74-43fc-b15d-52a557e79b8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e370425d-7d0c-4b2e-b6fe-727cdbe66032\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc1df064-233c-447b-9676-778a32e82b2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7e0a57d-4ba4-4a1d-96f0-6d7f405021a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 재단이 된다고 해도 재단으로 제작되면 밀림현상이 발생될 수 있습니다. 500장을 한 번에 재단하는 경우 밑에 있는 택은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f92cb76d-730e-4ef6-8509-3e845c3accfd\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>약 1~2mm 정도의 오차가 발생</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2269e59-7414-442d-a9da-d82f37fbbae4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">될 수 있습니다. 이점은 반드시 감안하여 주문하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-903f90b4-ef97-40ed-b4c9-9abc0bec1b4c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-01001208-959b-4895-99f2-ab3ae0c7f057\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6569d805-13f3-4213-b23a-79c6acabba79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-60a36a98-0957-430e-ba84-a160d82ec9b6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 고객 여러분이 정확한 택의 사이즈를 중요하게 생각하신다면 반드시 도무송(톰슨)으로 제작하시기 바랍니다, 하지만 일정 부분 단가는 포기해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce6a6ecd-865f-4f32-9303-e1987d671628\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19c3275f-6c7e-45b7-8e6f-07c77ea3c60e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54cb8988-b3bf-4714-a313-24bb3639b300\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-542be4ec-6872-45ce-bcfb-1567cca4ba4e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자유로운 모양의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-055fd400-d3a2-4839-8935-69434b57f911\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>모양택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-527918bb-8a09-4462-8460-e9450d4d6b74\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-544d0693-e0cd-46ce-94a8-f8d81077533a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-544d0693-e0cd-46ce-94a8-f8d81077533a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfMjc4/MDAxNzQ4MTQ0Mzc0NTIx.PYcSfzhyFfEWig_vg0H7dO5-PNySF7zLfdDmxBwHG_Ag.14ZIWDcqRjekuxlQOT2rlHQWjZ619vnWB26Og4WVurgg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1140\", \"originalHeight\" : \"556\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfMjc4/MDAxNzQ4MTQ0Mzc0NTIx.PYcSfzhyFfEWig_vg0H7dO5-PNySF7zLfdDmxBwHG_Ag.14ZIWDcqRjekuxlQOT2rlHQWjZ619vnWB26Og4WVurgg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5802d0f4-c1b3-4e8d-9e74-82375d941f40\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcb6b2bd-ee42-4c21-9e5f-d82fb7ed325c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0076a5d-6a60-4de0-ade9-fcd2ec618bd0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사각형의 모양보다는 더 자유롭게 택 모양을 만들 수 있습니다. 이는 조금 더 퀄리티를 고려한 제작 방식입니다. 위의 모양 말고도 더 자유로운 모양으로 제작이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-33702676-bfeb-4831-9d84-399660a3bb23\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:809px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-33702676-bfeb-4831-9d84-399660a3bb23\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfNDEg/MDAxNzQ4MTQ0OTUzNzI3.SP8wjM76s-Xo_W2WqJI38hntPV82aGVPz1FPjlEllWYg.uHz2ui-1WLTUwZ4b-RDzwFxZ_nCRo9TKvkwTE7Dsl3og.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"809\", \"originalHeight\" : \"518\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfNDEg/MDAxNzQ4MTQ0OTUzNzI3.SP8wjM76s-Xo_W2WqJI38hntPV82aGVPz1FPjlEllWYg.uHz2ui-1WLTUwZ4b-RDzwFxZ_nCRo9TKvkwTE7Dsl3og.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83a3cb1c-4b40-47e9-9cef-ba0c0380cddb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0c0bc5c4-66dc-4691-b31a-34a2f12781ca\" style=\"\">패키지 목형 샘플</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb96e16a-0d3d-4dfe-9cbe-62ffc150141c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56f1be26-571c-4c8c-bc17-fc4073cc3a2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b16bc91-191e-4d42-b17c-8182171d5ad4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위의 이미지대로 목형을 자유롭게 만들어서 택도 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-787293e4-a6ca-46de-8489-922635d48f17\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8dbdb8ac-63df-44df-ba50-b947658ab8d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-831b3060-bdd3-45d8-87cd-e8feba74bcee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93b189ad-09a1-485b-8f4e-91e81f4af666\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 목형을 만들어서 제작을 하면 몇 가지가 고려돼야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b136146d-075f-4e0d-a393-ab9793b2c4a9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6271ef47-1b90-4567-8733-f42dcac6ed47\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82103dc1-5e1c-4099-9a82-f5125bed2746\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-261a29ac-317a-4ddc-b14d-50c769aa6a33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 하나는 단가입니다. 일반 재단보다는 자유롭고 퀄리티가 높지만 목형 제작이나 도무송(톰슨)비용이 재단 비용보다는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-37932676-f72b-460b-9ea2-c629d8100148\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>훨씬 비쌉니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce4b7c3c-ec2a-4b6d-90e6-e5f21737c3c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 이 단가 부분을 반드시 감안하여 제작을 결정하십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8603ff0e-5753-4502-9e33-1a5bf7b980d3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4f65053-5ea3-42e9-a586-af34491a17fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b0308a1-7471-4b62-92b7-2814755e571e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fed9e4e2-950f-4875-bfa3-eb51c4a177f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 또 하나는 제작 기간입니다. 목형을 만드는 기간 도무송을 하는 기간까지 따지만 일반 재단보다 훨씬 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-39bd9a7f-1a54-4c9e-949c-8005951cefe0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>납기가 늦어집니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c46e3273-faea-49a3-84b2-86879efcaf70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21ada239-487e-46b8-882f-a961c6b6c50a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce1ca20a-cda1-4d5d-8512-31ae2525d82c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88f173c1-9409-4914-a50b-9d3e1c23327c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 단가와 남기가 단점일 수 있지만 퀄리티 면에서는 압도하고 또한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fba21937-d89c-49ff-985e-f38fc9ca7ef2\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>재 주문 시에는 목형 비용이 차감</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fef332e0-599b-46c0-844b-df1b83b2fdd7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">됩니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-fafe74b7-06f1-41a8-ad74-e29619b2e1de\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-be93f99f-ab16-4e4e-85ff-c1eb0c287bce\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82a4efe5-7563-41a2-8d6a-5eb42f7ff649\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-af492487-51eb-4446-9a88-d8ff5ad6ed86\" style=\"\">제작사양에 따른 맞춤 결정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-2ac0da0b-776f-4581-b2f8-00c1371b9352\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3036a8f1-1a39-4b88-88a2-d2bc0f630cac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54f58deb-f8db-43f3-9e00-3a254ee91e06\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5cad8117-a3c9-4c24-8a36-daa97f71cc92\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>여러분이 단가를 고려하신다면?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ada41b07-0fed-4c3c-a6d6-7d08d425a931\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-86e21f90-b310-412c-a7cf-855b31ebf781\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fbc8cce-6f85-476a-b7e5-4df8e48f225d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a44110d-8342-42fd-beb8-e70cf4b24e9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결론은 기본 모양과 최소 수량으로 제작하세요. 기본 모양은 사각형이고 최소 수량은 1개입니다. 샘플 제작 적이 아니라면 100개입니다. 단가에 최적화된 맞춤 수량은 1,000개 단위입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9524b69f-a9d9-4aa0-ba80-6dfeedef40c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08258c6b-07fc-45eb-9f99-8c312bb25a55\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92581da7-6773-475f-a364-de2d52d2e06a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4485462-110b-477a-ba8e-77a908ac7964\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 모양과 수량에 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7e15b04a-6353-4f73-a70d-2230950b3c58\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>단가가 중요하다면 사각형, 100개 단위로 주문</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-12dc9587-f96d-4572-aa3a-84a8f650b094\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-613d6b45-c6ab-400e-9ea7-a1d3dc8fde21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-13a276c5-8d87-4d23-a75f-f612dc0e640d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-825ed444-50ce-4059-886a-34411ce15fb9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55e63890-747b-49e7-997a-8ecf3bcdcc2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이도 일반적인 종이로 제작하세요. 일반적인 종이는 아트지/스노우지입니다. 평량은 250g이나 300g입니다. 가장 합리적인 가격을 제안 드릴 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-1e02ac45-8581-49a7-8328-9cb57f2cac54\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0896f73-ecca-4d89-aebe-8cf402f2efdb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82983a66-ece9-4849-8c3f-03f2b58d4d54\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e9a5e9ad-640e-4f79-a4fa-af97f2d987ff\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>여러분이 퀄리티가 더 중요하시다면?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d4c4b988-fca7-41ab-909a-6f85f31da405\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb44357f-426a-4f0b-b3a4-7ebcce4a8c26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc9e0d8d-42a5-4cbd-92cf-454d746de10b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6ebb6e5-758b-41d7-8ba3-59bf09f83d72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결론은 자유로운 모양과 소량으로 주문하세요. 자유로운 모양은 말 그대로 자유롭게 만드는 겁니다. 또한 수량은 소량으로 자주 발주하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76161764-4f8e-4215-823e-a3f797e59c7d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b69e906e-471c-4902-9c85-0371160cf242\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c8a68566-3263-4cff-b1c9-5ee78aa6895a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b3aa337-8902-4381-9774-be2d8b35441f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이도 완전히 선택적으로 제작할 수 있습니다. 수입지도 좋고 펄지도 좋습니다. 완전히 특별하게 만들 수 있고 또한 검은색 흑지로 제작하면서 백색 인쇄할 수도 있습니다. 정말 독특하게 만드실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19d99213-5beb-4f87-a74a-475fb6d0599f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-19d99213-5beb-4f87-a74a-475fb6d0599f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfNzMg/MDAxNzQ4MTQ3MTkxNDA1._EOUj86x5QhUqZwxowfYhNiTUBBXbHriquLEoZSPCPIg.gZTQ9Y4rvHo2Gs_Gly04bQSTz0IeOEfJhGHrd5kUbW8g.PNG/2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2002\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjVfNzMg/MDAxNzQ4MTQ3MTkxNDA1._EOUj86x5QhUqZwxowfYhNiTUBBXbHriquLEoZSPCPIg.gZTQ9Y4rvHo2Gs_Gly04bQSTz0IeOEfJhGHrd5kUbW8g.PNG/2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-1898706f-c42b-480a-9e2b-e15dc857fbfa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc6fc2ea-d788-40ff-baef-637a224b654d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5a97e18b-cd0a-4eba-8391-bba508f397bb\" style=\"\">반드시 문의하시고 주문하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c55e04b1-73a6-4323-aea8-9a27f0183b60\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56b5741f-97d3-4e5f-8ed9-1e65b121b585\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4d9b5bcb-4b6e-4306-8a45-4a3a0ddbb48b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택은 간단하게 제작할 수도 완전히 다른 단가와 방법으로 제작할 수도 있습니다. 이건 고객과의 소통에 의해 결정됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26ca5053-e891-4386-a322-5b8fd4ef13ec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-66dc7597-f6ed-4e39-b465-af4664573b16\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-859e5b9d-1299-438c-85c3-4b3f90c01ff8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8995f6b-eb49-4942-8c68-869f6abc7792\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 반드시 고객과의 소통을 통해 제안 드리겠습니다. 단가 절감 방법, 퀄리티를 높이는 방법은 꾸준하게 블로그 글로 알려드리지만 100% 일치한 정답을 말해드리지 못합니다. 이것은 고객님과의 소통으로 결정될 수 있습니다. 반드시 문의하시고 결정해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2d317abb-17c2-42d6-b7d8-5737702b2fba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-85ca3653-c63b-4ed2-a3a3-4d36e4f60137\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26c68206-1006-4ec8-864b-95882bc5eef3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24858f9f-6e14-4ddf-a073-02b92f110ac2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">헤더택도 거의 마찬가지 이야기로 정리하겠습니다. 헤더택도 규격 모양과 최소 수량이 중요합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223877065268#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
